<Action id="48863" issue="32832" author="kchristidis" type="comment" body="Remember that each channel results in the creation of a new Raft cluster. Need to ensure that a new cluster is created, even though this check is silly with only 1 node in the ensemble. Remember that client RPC invocations need to be tagged with the channel/cluster they belong to, and the server handler should maintain a mapping from cluster/channel to the appropriate Raft FSM." created="2018-08-14 18:07:07.0" updateauthor="kchristidis" updated="2018-08-14 18:07:07.0"/>
